  "errorHandling": [
    {
      "error": "Feed load fails",
      "display": "\"Unable to load feed. [Retry]\""
    },
    {
      "error": "Post fails",
      "display": "\"Unable to post. Please try again.\""
    },
    {
      "error": "Like/action fails",
      "display": "Toast: \"Action failed. Try again.\""
    }
  ],
  "analyticsEvents": [
    {
      "event": "`page_view`",
      "trigger": "Page load",
      "data": "feed_type"
    },
    {
      "event": "`post_created`",
      "trigger": "Post submitted",
      "data": "post_type, has_media"
    },
    {
      "event": "`post_liked`",
      "trigger": "Like clicked",
      "data": "post_id"
    },
    {
      "event": "`post_bookmarked`",
      "trigger": "Bookmark clicked",
      "data": "post_id"
    },
    {
      "event": "`post_replied`",
      "trigger": "Reply submitted",
      "data": "post_id"
    },
    {
      "event": "`post_reposted`",
      "trigger": "Repost clicked",
      "data": "post_id"
    },
    {
      "event": "`post_flagged`",
      "trigger": "Flag submitted",
      "data": "post_id, reason"
    },
    {
      "event": "`profile_clicked`",
      "trigger": "Author clicked",
      "data": "user_id"
    }
  ],
  "notes": [
    "**Stream.io integration:** Feed infrastructure via GetStream (CD-008)",
    "CD-013: 5 feed types documented in tech-002-stream.md",
    "Token generated server-side, never expose API secret to client",
    "Consider \"Mute\" feature for noisy users",
    "Moderation: Flagged posts go to MODQ (Stream + our moderation)",
    "Real-time updates via Stream's WebSocket infrastructure",
    "Hybrid DB+Stream ensures data durability and fast delivery"
